    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克反对派领袖表示准备暂停抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/mozambique-opposition-chief-signals-he-s-ready-to-pause-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克反对党领导人维南西奥·蒙德拉纳 (Venâncio Mondlane) 表示，尽管公务员计划罢工涨薪，但他愿意暂停困扰这个东南部非洲国家的抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/mozambique-opposition-chief-signals-he-s-ready-to-pause-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 14:03:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普威胁征收关税 欧盟与墨西哥签署贸易协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/eu-mexico-seal-trade-deal-as-trump-threatens-both-with-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在欧盟与墨西哥同意修订自由贸易协定之际，两国正面临当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的压力，特朗普威胁将对两国征收新一轮关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/eu-mexico-seal-trade-deal-as-trump-threatens-both-with-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 14:02:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥向特朗普献媚 打击对华贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/mexico-targets-chinese-trade-to-avoid-trump-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首先是墨西哥城一家以销售中国制造的服装、玩具和电子产品而闻名的购物中心遭到突击检查。然后，上个月，包括 Temu 和 Shein Group 在内的外国电子商务公司的包裹被征收近 20% 的关税，一些纺织品的关税甚至更高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/mexico-targets-chinese-trade-to-avoid-trump-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国需求增强，国际货币基金组织上调全球经济增长预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/imf-raises-global-economic-growth-forecast-on-stronger-us-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美国需求强于预期且全球通胀放缓的推动，国际货币基金组织上调了今年全球经济增长预测，这将使各国央行继续降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/imf-raises-global-economic-growth-forecast-on-stronger-us-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基与反对派会面，冷落斯洛伐克亲俄总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/zelenskiy-snubs-slovak-pro-russian-premier-by-meeting-opposition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基接待了一位越来越受欢迎的斯洛伐克反对派领导人，而基辅与斯洛伐克总理仍因天然气运输问题陷入争执。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/zelenskiy-snubs-slovak-pro-russian-premier-by-meeting-opposition</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 13:57:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普就职典礼前与中国国家主席习近平讨论贸易、TikTok</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/trump-and-china-s-xi-hold-phone-call-xinhua-news-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普和中国国家主席习近平周五在就职前的谈话中讨论了贸易、TikTok和芬太尼等问题，此次谈话可能为世界两大经济体和主要地缘政治对手之间的关系定下基调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/trump-and-china-s-xi-hold-phone-call-xinhua-news-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 13:51:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克里斯蒂娅·弗里兰 (Chrystia Freeland) 参加竞选，接替加拿大总理特鲁多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/ex-finance-minister-freeland-jumps-into-race-to-lead-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大前财政部长克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰 (Chrystia Freeland) 于 12 月辞职，结束了贾斯汀·特鲁多的政治生涯，如今她已加入继任总理的竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/ex-finance-minister-freeland-jumps-into-race-to-lead-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 13:16:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨否认将自身政治生存置于支持乌克兰之上的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/german-chancellor-scholz-denies-prioritizing-relection-over-support-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨反驳了有关他抛弃乌克兰以在下个月提前选举前为落后的社会民主党争取支持的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/german-chancellor-scholz-denies-prioritizing-relection-over-support-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 12:11:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>基辅称俄罗斯对克里沃罗格的袭击造成平民死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/kyiv-says-three-killed-in-russian-missile-strike-on-kryvyi-rih</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰中部城市克里沃罗格州长谢尔盖·莱萨克在电报中表示，俄罗斯弹道导弹袭击乌克兰中部城市克里沃罗格，造成 4 人死亡，至少 7 人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/kyiv-says-three-killed-in-russian-missile-strike-on-kryvyi-rih</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 11:10:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>出生于莫斯科的前特朗普助手菲利克斯·萨特获得新的洗钱审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/ex-trump-associate-felix-sater-wins-new-money-laundering-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[费利克斯·萨特（Felix Sater）是一位备受争议的房地产经纪人，曾是候任总统唐纳德·特朗普的核心圈子成员，他在哈萨克斯坦银行针对他提起的民事洗钱诉讼中，在纽约赢得了重新审判的胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/ex-trump-associate-felix-sater-wins-new-money-laundering-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 22:23:42 GMT</pubDate>
